## Color System

### Gray Scale
- `gray-50` through `gray-900` (lightest to darkest)
- Use for: backgrounds, borders, text

### Brand Colors
- `blue-*` - Primary actions
- `green-*` - Success states
- `red-*` - Errors, destructive actions
- `yellow-*` - Warnings
- `purple-*`, `pink-*`, `indigo-*` - Accents

### Usage
```html
<!-- Text colors -->
<p class="text-gray-900">Primary text</p>
<p class="text-gray-600">Secondary text</p>
<p class="text-gray-400">Tertiary text</p>

<!-- Background colors -->
<div class="bg-blue-600">Primary background</div>
<div class="bg-gray-50">Light background</div>

<!-- Border colors -->
<div class="border border-gray-300">Border</div>
<div class="border-2 border-blue-500">Emphasized border</div>
```

